        Our<br />Projects
      </h1>
    </div>
    <div class="cnt-projects-description">
      <p class="projects-description">
        home designed to combine simplicity and functionality with a sleek,
        timeless aesthetic. The project aimed to create an open, airy living
        space that maximizes natural light while maintaining a clutter-free and
        sophisticated environment.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section>
    <TabsNavegation client:load />
  </section>

  <!-- Section Two -->

  <section class="image-gallery-section">
    <h2 class="gallery-title">Our gallery</h2>

    <div class="gallery-grid">
      <div class="gallery-item">
        <img
          src="/images/remoKitchenHome.jpg"
          alt="ProyectKitchen"
          class="gallery-image"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="gallery-item">
